Name: Stitches two string being concatenated if placed at the beginning of the second one
Point-Char: |
Code: (lambda ()
       (php-mode)
       (php-fill-backward-delete))
=-=
$stringVar = 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit '
    . '|amet, consectetur.';
=-=
$stringVar = 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit|amet, consectetur.';
=-=-=

